te this approach with a number of examples, including a stable\nlocalization of a persistent homology generator from brain imaging data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Dec 2015 20:42:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2017 23:56:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 22 Dec 2017 02:55:38 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 25 Oct 2018 15:02:40 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 16 Oct 2019 19:39:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-29"}
