re limited. Moreover, it suggests that the proposed Bayesian\nframework is an effective way to incorporate empirical knowledge from various\nsources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Dec 2015 06:23:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-25"}
